ope,\nthe per-entity JMS pipeline (entity serialization, JSON serialization,\npublish, consume, deserialize) ran only to discard every message since\nno external consumer can connect to the embedded broker.\n\nWith default configuration this disables tracker audit (logger off via\nhardcoded fallback in TrackerAuditConsumer, database off globally) while\nleaving metadata and aggregate audit enabled (logger defaults to on).\n\nAlso check the audit matrix in Hibernate listeners before building the\nAudit object. Previously the check only happened inside\nAuditManager.send(), after the expensive createAuditEntry() work (schema\nlookup, entity state serialization). This benefits all scopes.\n\nAdditional cleanups:\n- Simplify audit matrix from Map\u003cAuditType, Boolean\u003e to Set\u003cAuditType\u003e\n- Fail on invalid audit type config instead of silently ignoring\n- Handle DISABLED as an explicit token (was working by accident)\n- Trim whitespace in audit type config values\n- Fix test config using wrong separator (CREATE_UPDATE_DELETE instead of\n  CREATE;UPDATE;DELETE)","author":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"ea66241c87cd2b50ee2c77364f2fc0445ef79912","tree_id":"cddac9021d984afef73c1d076135eace8cdaec40","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:22:40Z","committer":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.